1
00:00:05,394 --> 00:00:07,403
"Berdasarkan kisah 'Tale of On Dal in Chronicles of the Three States'."

2
00:00:07,404 --> 00:00:09,400
"Watak, insiden dan tarikh tidak sepadan dengan fakta bersejarah."

3
00:00:10,504 --> 00:00:11,634
Pemberontakan?

4
00:00:11,635 --> 00:00:14,544
Kota Juam memberontak?

5
00:00:14,545 --> 00:00:17,244
"Sebelum ini..."

6
00:00:17,245 --> 00:00:19,270
Saya akan terus ketuai tentera kita.

7
00:00:20,484 --> 00:00:21,913
Pergi semula ke Istana Pyeongyang.

8
00:00:21,914 --> 00:00:24,509
Kita tak tahu apa yang Go Won Pyo dan anaknya mungkin lakukan.

9
00:00:24,655 --> 00:00:26,214
Hanya awak saja yang boleh halang mereka.

10
00:00:26,215 --> 00:00:27,619
Tuanku...

11
00:00:27,925 --> 00:00:31,150
Mulai sekarang, saya akan hukum pengkhianat atas kesalahannya.

12
00:00:31,754 --> 00:00:33,224
Apa maksud awak dia ditahan?

13
00:00:33,225 --> 00:00:35,559
Maklumkan Puak Gwanno dan Sono segera.

14
00:00:36,265 --> 00:00:37,659
Suruh mereka bersenjata...

15
00:00:38,094 --> 00:00:39,993
...dan pergi ke istana.

16
00:00:39,994 --> 00:00:41,133
Semuanya dah berakhir, Tuan Go.

17
00:00:41,134 --> 00:00:43,360
Hanya rancangan ayah saya saja yang berakhir.

18
00:00:44,305 --> 00:00:46,173
Rancangan saya masih belum bermula lagi.

19
00:00:46,174 --> 00:00:47,500
Menyerah sajalah, Tuan Go.

20
00:00:58,685 --> 00:01:01,519
Datanglah pada saya kalau awak nak mati!

21
00:01:04,395 --> 00:01:05,490
Pecah masuk penjara?

22
00:01:05,494 --> 00:01:08,094
Itu bukan tanggungjawab saya untuk bebaskan dia dan ayahnya.

23
00:01:08,095 --> 00:01:09,460
Apabila keadaan berubah...

24
00:01:10,024 --> 00:01:12,359
...janji juga boleh diubah.

25
00:01:14,964 --> 00:01:16,859
Saya akan pergi jika awak suruh saya pergi...

26
00:01:18,705 --> 00:01:20,070
...dan berhenti jika awak mahu saya berhenti.

27
00:01:24,574 --> 00:01:27,440
"Episod 17"

28
00:01:28,914 --> 00:01:30,484
- Hei! - Lepaskan saya!

29
00:01:30,485 --> 00:01:31,984
Lepaskan saya!

30
00:01:31,985 --> 00:01:34,454
- Lepaskan saya! - Kenapa saya ada di sini?

31
00:01:34,455 --> 00:01:36,653
- Diam! - Lepaskan saya!

32
00:01:36,654 --> 00:01:38,619
Go Won Pyo, anaknya, Go Geon...

33
00:01:38,955 --> 00:01:42,119
...dan semua askar Puak Gyeru dipenjarakan.

34
00:01:42,764 --> 00:01:45,430
Puak Gyeru patut berkhidmat sebagai tulang belakang empayar kita...

35
00:01:45,434 --> 00:01:47,029
...tapi mereka menderhaka?

36
00:01:47,264 --> 00:01:49,630
Mereka semua mesti dipancung.

37
00:01:50,574 --> 00:01:54,469
Keluarga Go berdarah diraja.

38
00:01:55,274 --> 00:01:57,139
Mudah untuk memancung mereka...

39
00:01:57,774 --> 00:02:00,979
...tapi kita tak boleh rosakkan reputasi kita.

40
00:02:01,285 --> 00:02:03,009
Tapi tuanku...

41
00:02:03,755 --> 00:02:05,314
Ada apa-apa berita daripada Puak Sono?

42
00:02:05,315 --> 00:02:08,219
Tuan Hae Ji Weol dan anaknya sudah menghilangkan diri.

43
00:02:08,885 --> 00:02:11,719
Saya dah suruh orang cari tempat di mana mereka mungkin menyorok.

44
00:02:19,295 --> 00:02:22,260
Keluarga Go mungkin berdarah diraja,...

45
00:02:22,434 --> 00:02:26,033
...tapi jenayah penderhakaan adalah lebih berat.

46
00:02:26,034 --> 00:02:27,140
Begitulah.

47
00:02:28,504 --> 00:02:30,539
Betul kata Tuan Jin.

48
00:02:35,015 --> 00:02:37,980
Tuanku perlu tunjukkan keazaman.

49
00:02:46,724 --> 00:02:51,089
Awak tamatkan rawatan dan balik awal.

50
00:02:51,365 --> 00:02:53,260
Jangan cakap...

51
00:02:54,004 --> 00:02:55,563
...apa-apa lagi.

52
00:02:55,564 --> 00:02:58,129
Awak tipu saya dan ayah saya...

53
00:02:58,434 --> 00:03:00,604
...dan sekarang awak bangga dengan diri sendiri.

54
00:03:00,605 --> 00:03:01,700
Jadi...

55
00:03:02,605 --> 00:03:06,339
Patutkah saya kurung awak di sebelah Go Won Pyo?

56
00:03:07,314 --> 00:03:08,409
Apa...

57
00:03:16,055 --> 00:03:18,824
Keadaan awak dah bertambah baik?

58
00:03:18,825 --> 00:03:19,920
Ya.

59
00:03:21,395 --> 00:03:25,230
Disebabkan keprihatinan tuanku, saya dah sembuh sepenuhnya.

60
00:03:27,464 --> 00:03:30,330
Tuhan dah bantu awak. Baguslah.

61
00:03:31,004 --> 00:03:34,339
Putera sering bertanya tentang awak.

62
00:03:34,944 --> 00:03:36,300
Saya minta maaf.

63
00:03:36,874 --> 00:03:40,069
Ayah dah buat keputusan untuk uruskan Go Won Pyo dan anaknya?

64
00:03:43,015 --> 00:03:44,950
Esok pada waktu subuh,...

65
00:03:46,085 --> 00:03:48,080
...mereka akan dipancung.

66
00:04:04,335 --> 00:04:06,473
- Kita dah sampai? - Ya.

67
00:04:06,474 --> 00:04:08,843
Helo. Awak sangat comel.

68
00:04:08,844 --> 00:04:11,610
Weol, mari sini.

69
00:04:11,944 --> 00:04:13,473
- Baik. - Ada banyak benda cantik.

70
00:04:13,474 --> 00:04:15,943
Mari kita datang kemudian dan lihat.

71
00:04:15,944 --> 00:04:17,380
- Saya dah sampai. - Baik.

72
00:04:19,285 --> 00:04:20,620
Saya terlepas lagi.

73
00:04:21,985 --> 00:04:23,179
Macam mana patut saya bidik?

74
00:04:26,494 --> 00:04:27,589
Abang Dal?

75
00:04:29,595 --> 00:04:31,989
- Ya? - Awak dan Kak Pyeonggang bergaduh?

76
00:04:33,235 --> 00:04:34,503
Tak adalah.

77
00:04:34,504 --> 00:04:37,669
Saya ingat kamu berdua bertengkar tentang Tuan Go.

78
00:04:38,004 --> 00:04:40,370
Dia kata dia akan setia kepada kita tapi dia menderhaka.

79
00:04:41,244 --> 00:04:42,570
Berani dia?

80
00:04:43,305 --> 00:04:45,469
Awak patut bunuh dia.

81
00:04:46,644 --> 00:04:49,339
Saya dengar awak dah bunuh lebih 100 orang dalam pertempuran.

82
00:04:49,514 --> 00:04:52,450
Bagaimana rasanya? Tentu awak rasa sangat puas hati.

83
00:04:57,124 --> 00:04:58,919
Awak nak tahu apa perasaannya...

84
00:05:01,494 --> 00:05:02,719
...untuk membunuh seseorang?

85
00:05:09,465 --> 00:05:11,000
Kosongkan dada, penuhkan perut.

86
00:05:11,434 --> 00:05:12,529
Apa yang awak buat?

87
00:05:16,405 --> 00:05:17,774
Apabila menggunakan busur,...

88
00:05:17,775 --> 00:05:20,414
Kosongkan hati awak, kuatkan perut awak...

89
00:05:20,415 --> 00:05:21,979
...dan bidik.

90
00:05:22,845 --> 00:05:24,279
Apa yang awak buat?

91
00:05:24,555 --> 00:05:25,650
Lepaskan saya.

92
00:05:26,884 --> 00:05:28,719
Leher atau jantung.

93
00:05:29,985 --> 00:05:32,250
Itu akan tamatkan riwayatnya dengan segera.

94
00:05:33,254 --> 00:05:34,419
Awak dah gilakah?

95
00:05:34,795 --> 00:05:35,890
Jeneral!

96
00:06:07,025 --> 00:06:10,263
Awak patut beritahu kami kalau awak nak datang.

97
00:06:10,264 --> 00:06:12,993
Kami akan hantar tandu atau pedati.

98
00:06:12,994 --> 00:06:14,703
Perjalanan awak tentu sukar.

99
00:06:14,704 --> 00:06:16,833
Saya tak sesuai naik tandu.

100
00:06:16,834 --> 00:06:19,933
Awak mak mentua puteri Goguryeo...

101
00:06:19,934 --> 00:06:21,900
...dan mak kepada jeneral.

102
00:06:22,074 --> 00:06:26,344
Sebelum ini, Dal pergi bunuh pengkhianat...

103
00:06:26,345 --> 00:06:29,013
...dan kembali dengan kemenangan yang besar.

104
00:06:29,014 --> 00:06:30,654
- Ya. - Betul.

105
00:06:30,655 --> 00:06:32,409
- Dia bunuh orang? - Ya.

106
00:06:36,584 --> 00:06:38,650
- Begitu. - Ke tepi.

107
00:06:40,425 --> 00:06:44,960
Nampaknya awak guna tongkat yang saya buat untuk awak.

108
00:06:45,134 --> 00:06:47,433
Ia bagus dan kecil, sesuai untuk saya.

109
00:06:47,434 --> 00:06:50,364
Jadi awak tak sakit?

110
00:06:50,365 --> 00:06:53,169
Adakah saya akan datang ke sini kalau saya sakit?

111
00:06:54,574 --> 00:06:55,799
Jadi...

112
00:06:56,944 --> 00:07:02,013
...saya boleh tahu daripada suara awak yang awak hidup dengan baik.

113
00:07:02,014 --> 00:07:03,839
Sikit saja.

114
00:07:05,555 --> 00:07:09,823
Betul. Awak nampak macam orang bandar.

115
00:07:09,824 --> 00:07:11,950
Weol, tentu awak rasa sukar.

116
00:07:13,754 --> 00:07:16,493
Dulu awak sekecil kacang pis...

117
00:07:16,494 --> 00:07:18,294
...dan sekarang awak dah besar.

118
00:07:18,295 --> 00:07:20,234
Jangan sentuh saya.

119
00:07:20,235 --> 00:07:23,164
Berani awak pegang pipi seorang wanita dewasa?

120
00:07:23,165 --> 00:07:24,370
Awak dah dewasa?

121
00:07:26,204 --> 00:07:28,404
- Dal! - Aduhai.

122
00:07:28,405 --> 00:07:29,870
- Apa khabar? - Dal ada di sini.

123
00:07:34,884 --> 00:07:36,010
Mak.

124
00:07:36,985 --> 00:07:38,109
Dal?

125
00:07:41,124 --> 00:07:42,183
Mak.

126
00:07:42,184 --> 00:07:45,320
Biar saya jumpa anak saya. Peluk saya.

127
00:07:45,725 --> 00:07:46,820
Mak.

128
00:07:47,225 --> 00:07:50,489
Ya Tuhan... Anak mak...

129
00:07:51,994 --> 00:07:53,289
Mak.

130
00:07:55,004 --> 00:07:56,099
Ya.

131
00:07:58,975 --> 00:08:01,299
Ya. Ini mak kamu.

132
00:08:01,905 --> 00:08:04,109
Saya datang nak jumpa kamu.

133
00:08:04,744 --> 00:08:06,710
Saya rindukan mak juga.

134
00:08:06,775 --> 00:08:10,409
Mak tahu. Sebab itulah mak datang ke sini.

135
00:08:13,355 --> 00:08:14,450
Kamu menangiskah?

136
00:08:15,485 --> 00:08:16,679
Tidak.

137
00:08:17,225 --> 00:08:19,450
Orang akan fikir seseorang dah mati.

138
00:08:20,454 --> 00:08:21,693
Berhenti menangis.

139
00:08:21,694 --> 00:08:23,359
Saya tak menangis.

140
00:08:25,365 --> 00:08:27,664
Kenapa pula jeneral besar Goguryeo...

141
00:08:27,665 --> 00:08:30,969
...menangis di tempat awam dan malukan diri sendiri?

142
00:08:32,305 --> 00:08:34,804
- Aduhai. - Mak.

143
00:08:34,805 --> 00:08:38,870
Mak tahu. Mak ada di sini.

144
00:08:41,015 --> 00:08:42,183
Ya.

145
00:08:42,184 --> 00:08:43,544
Saya sangat rindukan mak.

146
00:08:43,545 --> 00:08:46,409
Ya, mak tahu.

147
00:08:49,655 --> 00:08:50,924
Bagus dan rata, bukan?

148
00:08:50,925 --> 00:08:53,554
Ya. Batu pun tak ada.

149
00:08:53,555 --> 00:08:54,659
Betul.

150
00:08:55,495 --> 00:08:56,590
Mak.

151
00:09:01,405 --> 00:09:03,833
Dah berapa lama kita tak berjumpa?

152
00:09:03,834 --> 00:09:05,874
Kamu tak apa-apa?

153
00:09:05,875 --> 00:09:06,970
Ya.

154
00:09:24,094 --> 00:09:26,090
Rasa selesa dan hangat.

155
00:09:26,354 --> 00:09:30,059
Maafkan saya, mak. Saya patut bawa mak lebih awal.

156
00:09:30,364 --> 00:09:32,693
Mak tak percaya mak ada di istana ini.

157
00:09:32,694 --> 00:09:35,100
Bagaikan mimpi.

158
00:09:35,334 --> 00:09:37,529
Kami tinggal di sini, mak.

159
00:09:37,734 --> 00:09:39,770
Ia luas dan bagus, bukan?

160
00:09:40,135 --> 00:09:44,140
Nampaknya begitulah. Setiap pelusuk juga berbau harum.

161
00:09:45,314 --> 00:09:48,083
Mak datang dari jauh. Rehatlah sementara mak di sini.

162
00:09:48,084 --> 00:09:49,740
Mak tak patut berehat.

163
00:09:50,714 --> 00:09:55,819
Mak dengar ada kekecohan berlaku di dalam istana.

164
00:09:58,655 --> 00:10:02,220
Semuanya dah berakhir. Jeneral On tanganinya dengan baik.

165
00:10:03,724 --> 00:10:06,260
Kamu maksudkan bunuh penderhaka?

166
00:10:07,464 --> 00:10:09,230
Mana mak tahu tentang itu?

167
00:10:10,135 --> 00:10:12,304
Adakah Hong Mae yang beritahu?

168
00:10:12,305 --> 00:10:13,733
Atau Pil Gu?

169
00:10:13,734 --> 00:10:16,304
Kenapa kamu marah sangat?

170
00:10:16,305 --> 00:10:17,569
Saya tak marah.

171
00:10:17,814 --> 00:10:18,909
Dal.

172
00:10:22,745 --> 00:10:26,583
Mak. Apa kata mak berpindah ke bandar?

173
00:10:26,584 --> 00:10:28,683
Kami akan carikan tempat untuk mak tinggal.

174
00:10:28,684 --> 00:10:29,880
Tak apalah.

175
00:10:30,584 --> 00:10:32,525
Ia mungkin pondok yang hampir runtuh...

176
00:10:32,525 --> 00:10:34,425
...tapi mak ada rumah sendiri.

177
00:10:34,425 --> 00:10:36,824
Kami akan rasa lebih tenang jika mak tinggal berdekatan.

178
00:10:36,824 --> 00:10:39,090
Mak hargai niat kamu.

179
00:10:39,135 --> 00:10:42,329
Tapi, fikirkanlah masak-masak.

180
00:10:43,635 --> 00:10:44,929
Jangan paksa dia.

181
00:10:45,604 --> 00:10:47,169
Dia tak nak.

182
00:10:49,944 --> 00:10:51,340
Tuan puteri.

183
00:10:54,245 --> 00:10:56,179
Perjalanan puan pasti jauh.

184
00:10:57,114 --> 00:10:59,484
Dia pengasuh saya dan dia dah macam keluarga saya.

185
00:10:59,484 --> 00:11:02,880
Aduhai. Terima kasih banyak.

186
00:11:03,454 --> 00:11:05,155
Saya hanya dayang istana.

187
00:11:05,155 --> 00:11:06,620
Kesopanan tak diperlukan.

188
00:11:07,125 --> 00:11:11,829
Tuan puteri. Raja mahu berjumpa Puan Sa.

189
00:11:12,765 --> 00:11:13,929
Ayah saya?

190
00:11:15,964 --> 00:11:18,834
Beta nak tahu tentang wanita yang besarkan Jeneral On dengan baik...

191
00:11:18,834 --> 00:11:20,199
...jadi beta nak jumpa kamu.

192
00:11:20,535 --> 00:11:22,305
Terima kasih, tuanku.

193
00:11:22,305 --> 00:11:24,245
Ketika saya dalam masalah besar...

194
00:11:24,245 --> 00:11:26,209
...dia jaga saya dengan baik.

195
00:11:27,614 --> 00:11:30,114
Dia juga marah saya seperti mana-mana mak mentua lain.

196
00:11:30,114 --> 00:11:31,209
Anakku.

197
00:11:31,814 --> 00:11:34,279
Tuanku, ketika itu...

198
00:11:36,025 --> 00:11:38,789
...saya hanya marah dia sedikit sahaja.

199
00:11:41,464 --> 00:11:43,694
Puteri yang tak takut apa-apa...

200
00:11:43,694 --> 00:11:46,059
...bagaikan buku bertemu ruas dengan mak mentuanya.

201
00:11:48,505 --> 00:11:50,564
Beta kagum dengan apa yang kamu buat...

202
00:11:50,564 --> 00:11:52,130
...walaupun kamu buta.

203
00:11:52,604 --> 00:11:56,740
Wanita Goguryeo patut anggap kamu sebagai contoh dan belajar.

204
00:11:57,474 --> 00:11:58,569
Oleh itu,...

205
00:11:59,145 --> 00:12:03,709
...beta nak beri dia barang kemas dan kain.

206
00:12:03,885 --> 00:12:06,179
Itu satu penghormatan besar.

207
00:12:08,025 --> 00:12:11,689
Tawaran tuanku melebihi apa yang saya layak terima.

208
00:12:12,755 --> 00:12:14,150
Daripada menerima ganjaran...

209
00:12:15,464 --> 00:12:18,890
...saya nak minta satu permintaan yang mudah.

210
00:12:19,165 --> 00:12:20,260
Permintaan?

211
00:12:21,464 --> 00:12:23,860
Beritahu beta apa saja.

212
00:12:27,405 --> 00:12:29,000
Anak saya On Dal.

213
00:12:30,405 --> 00:12:35,779
Benarkan dia pulang ke rumah bersama saya pada hari ini.

214
00:12:39,915 --> 00:12:41,020
Mak.

215
00:12:41,125 --> 00:12:42,720
Dia membesar dengan alam semula jadi...

216
00:12:43,224 --> 00:12:45,720
...dengan tanah sebagai tilam dan langit sebagai selimutnya.

217
00:12:48,425 --> 00:12:50,890
Saya dengar dia dah berkhidmat untuk negaranya dengan baik.

218
00:12:51,734 --> 00:12:53,760
Tolong benarkan dia kembali ke alam semula jadi...

219
00:12:54,434 --> 00:12:56,559
...dan hidup bebas.

220
00:13:08,844 --> 00:13:10,840
Bila saya kata saya nak balik rumah?

221
00:13:11,915 --> 00:13:14,454
Isteri saya ada di sini, begitu juga dengan kawan-kawan saya.

222
00:13:14,454 --> 00:13:16,049
Saya hidup dan makan dengan baik di sini.

223
00:13:16,285 --> 00:13:18,155
Lebih baik daripada yang mak risaukan.

224
00:13:18,155 --> 00:13:19,724
Dal, hentikannya.

225
00:13:19,724 --> 00:13:21,620
Mak yang patut berhenti.

226
00:13:23,964 --> 00:13:26,434
Saya tertanya-tanya kenapa mak datang ke bandar.

227
00:13:26,434 --> 00:13:28,035
Rupanya mak datang ke sini untuk cakap perkara mengarut.

228
00:13:28,035 --> 00:13:29,760
Mak kenal kamu.

229
00:13:30,135 --> 00:13:32,334
Kamu mungkin berpangkat tinggi dan hidup dengan baik...

230
00:13:32,334 --> 00:13:34,199
...tapi itu tak buat kamu gembira.

231
00:13:34,545 --> 00:13:37,199
Hidup mak tak sehebat orang lain...

232
00:13:38,545 --> 00:13:40,844
...tapi Dal, mak cuba bantu kamu bernafas.

233
00:13:40,844 --> 00:13:42,079
Sebagai mak kamu.

234
00:13:42,184 --> 00:13:43,214
Saya dah tak tahan.

235
00:13:43,214 --> 00:13:44,309
Dal.

236
00:13:48,155 --> 00:13:52,449
Saya tiada niat untuk kembali ke gunung.

237
